{"tid":2422122,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"查理芒格：GME炒作如賭馬","createTime":"2021-02-25T03:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T03:58:20.000Z","uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b366d1b630166a41965074f89cefdb320b360bbe","tid":2422122,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:35:21.000Z","msg":"股神巴菲特旗下投資旗艦巴郡副主席芒格警告，股市有泡沫跡象，認為散戶炒作GameStop（GME）的行為有如賭馬，對於這種賭博的文化感到愚蠢。<br />\n<br />\nGameStop炒作過程中，證券商Robinhood扮演一個重要角色。芒格說，不要以為Robinhood真的是在為散戶提供免費炒股服務。他認為，投資者單純見到股價急升，就撲入股市投資，這種瘋狂買股行為，本身是一種十分危險的投資手法。芒格指出，誘惑「賭徒」進入股市，本質是「骯髒」的獲利手段；金融體系內卑鄙手段十分多，造成大量投資新手入場，並帶來巨量交易。<br />\n<br />\n對於比特幣近日急升，芒格稱，不會像電動車生產商Tesla（TSLA )那樣買入比特幣，又認為比特幣波動性太高，難以成為全球交易媒介。他建議投資者不要買比特幣或黃金。另外，芒格表示美國國債市場並不存在泡沫，價值投資也從來都不會過時。<br />\n<br />\nGameStop股價昨晚（24日）再度爆升，最新報91.71美元，升46.74美元或104％。"},{"pid":"5e4fbe769b2765ae682c3acaba0206c5fa6164ce","tid":2422122,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:36:01.000Z","msg":"廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16251858ae68ad85d4b8e640ab9dcab715360da","tid":2422122,"uid":62247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:37:54.000Z","msg":"又想搞鳩隻股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1520416729ba64dbee104978bd497393580ac6ca","tid":2422122,"uid":89037,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:49:02.000Z","msg":"WSB 本身就係賭博<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你會唔會去馬會屌柒人地賭錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7be8f38dc4f3a0f329421e54ee8e08d707d496","tid":2422122,"uid":5289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:49:57.000Z","msg":"佢淡倉好多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cbd4f3e6d5558607d0f662b37e5370a3ec27146","tid":2422122,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:50:49.000Z","msg":"但係賭馬可以靜靜哋贏喎⋯⋯"},{"pid":"469c61c756a1f1400c23f0cfd0ba9b83747f54b8","tid":2422122,"uid":219742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:51:22.000Z","msg":"睇英文版， 佢應該係話緊班空頭賭錢"},{"pid":"eeb754cde099aed6402f7ec2626fa8cfe4cf2127","tid":2422122,"uid":57462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:51:57.000Z","msg":"賭馬起碼有路捉有數據支持, GME 真係純粹心理炒起"},{"pid":"76fa3e43a7aab70faf24498363062be041eae5f7","tid":2422122,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:52:39.000Z","msg":"不停借人股賣都係賭錢"},{"pid":"e281ac6196af89780eea4a5e11c4a09a495994e9","tid":2422122,"uid":136147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1520416729ba64dbee104978bd497393580ac6ca","tid":2422122,"uid":89037,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:49:02.000Z","msg":"WSB 本身就係賭博<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你會唔會去馬會屌柒人地賭錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T03:58:20.000Z","msg":"Wall Street BET 人地都開宗名義唔係玩價投"}]}